Feature: TC_01_STAFF - Map Printing by Herd Number E2E Regression Pack

  # --------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
  # Purpose:
  #   Single end-to-end regression journey covering Map Printing by Herd Number Search on the
  #   BISS Staff (internal) portal. Consolidates the legacy multi-scenario Map-Printing-with-Herd
  #   pack (AT-TC-01, AT-TC-02, AT-TC-04) into one continuous E2E flow.
  #
  #   Sections covered:
  #     Section 1 : Generate map by herd - single parcel change   (legacy AT-TC-01)
  #     Section 2 : Herd number required validation                (legacy AT-TC-02)
  #     Section 3 : Generate map by herd - all parcels selected    (legacy AT-TC-04)
  #
  # Migrated from: Feature "Regression Suite for Map Printing with Herd" (3 separate scenarios)
  #
  # Modernisation notes:
  #   - Login block collapsed into Background (was repeated in every scenario)
  #   - Herd values now supplied via DataTable in the feature (no "from row N" DB coupling)
  #   - Search + generate settings expressed as DataTables for readability
  #   - Env-dependent map generation left as-is; validation steps are soft where optional
  #
  # Author : Aniket Pathare | aniket.pathare@government.ie
  # Created: 14-07-2026
  # --------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

  Background:
    Given user on staff login page
    When Staff logs in with the following credentials
      | username        | agr11612 |
    And Staff opens the "Basic Income Support for Sustainability" application
    And Staff switches to the "Map Printing" tab

  @regression @staff @map-printing @herd @e2e
  Scenario: AT-STAFF-MAP-HERD-E2E-01 - Staff generates maps by herd number and validates required-field errors

    # ===========================================
    # SECTION 1 : Generate map by herd (single parcel change)
    # Covers: AT-TC-01  (BISSAGL-14969)
    # ===========================================
    When Staff searches on the Map Printing screen with the following details
      | field       | herdNumber |
      | herdValue   | N106036X   |
      | schemeYear  | 2023       |
    And Staff changes the "parcelSelect" multi-option dropdown value
    And Staff selects the following map generation settings
      | mapTypeSelect | Full Color Ortho A4 |
    And Staff clicks the Legend Indicator checkbox
    Then Staff clicks the "Generate map" button

    # ===========================================
    # SECTION 2 : Herd number required validation
    # Covers: AT-TC-02  (BISSAGL-14968)
    # ===========================================
    When Staff switches to the "Map Printing" tab
    And Staff clicks the "Search" button
    Then Staff should see the error message "Herd number required."

    # ===========================================
    # SECTION 3 : Generate map by herd (all parcels selected)
    # Covers: AT-TC-04  (BISSAGL-14966)
    # ===========================================
    When Staff searches on the Map Printing screen with the following details
      | field       | herdNumber |
      | herdValue   | N106036X   |
      | schemeYear  | 2023       |
    And Staff selects all values in the "parcelSelect" multi-option dropdown
    And Staff selects the following map generation settings
      | mapTypeSelect | Full Color Ortho A4 |
    And Staff clicks the Legend Indicator checkbox
    Then Staff clicks the "Generate map" button
